tool_description: Sportsbook API is a sports betting API which provides up to the minute odds for 10 major US sportsbooks across 20 different sports leagues.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sportsbook-api2.p.rapidapi.com/v0/events/kXuc-xfma-eRVR/markets"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sportsbook-api2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
